Final SQL query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ml.Model) AS CarModelCount FROM model_list AS ml JOIN car_makers AS cm ON ml.Maker = cm.Id JOIN countries AS c ON cm.Country = c.CountryId WHERE c.CountryName COLLATE NOCASE = 'United States';
