Final SQL query: SELECT DISTINCT ml.Model FROM model_list AS ml JOIN car_makers AS cm ON ml.Maker = cm.Id JOIN cars_data AS cd ON ml.ModelId = cd.Id WHERE cm.FullName COLLATE NOCASE = 'General Motors' AND cd.Weight > 3500;
Final execution result: passed
