*   **"weighing no less than 3000"**: This translates to a condition on the `Weight` column in the `cars_data` table ( `Weight >= 3000`).
*   **"no more than 4000"**: This translates to another condition on the `Weight` column in the `cars_data` table (`Weight <= 4000`).
*   **"years"**: This refers to the `Year` column in the `cars_data` table.

